This directory contains base class templates for classes that define the 
domain or contain or manipulate fields for systems with periodic boundary 
conditions.  Classes with names that end in the suffix "Real" are designed 
for systems with real fields, for use in the Rpc and Rpg namespaces, and
the pscf_pc and pscf_pg programs.

Classes:

  DomainReal  - base class template for (Rpc|Rpg)::Domain
  FieldIoReal - base class template for (Rpc|Rpg)::FieldIo
  WFieldsReal - base class template for (Rpc|Rpg)::WFieldContainer 
  CFieldsReal - base class template for (Rpc|Rpg)::CFieldContainer 
  MaskTmpl    - base class template for (Rpc|Rpg)::Mask

Files that define global function templates:

  fieldIoUtil.h    - functions used in FieldIoReal
  fieldArrayUtil.h - utilities field containers
    
